message.body: Yesterday wasn't bad... Had a meeting with architect to go over the house. Designing it the way we want it. Today I'm up at the Crowne. Gloomy day... How are you?
That's exciting! Where's the Crowne? I'm going to eat something. My exam is today...yikes.
Princeton. Good luck!
Haha. Sorry about that. Let me know how it goes.
Hahah I'm so used to you saying "Princeton" that it threw me when you said "Crowne".
Thanks!
I'm probably going to be so exhausted, good luck to you trying to understand me while I try to form words hahah!
It's going to be that extensive? You should be fine...
They said it's going to take 2-3 hours.
When is the test?
I'm taking it now. I'm on a bathroom break. Steve I hate it. It's friggin' hard!
No... I was gonna sleep too.
Is it too early for bed?
Hahah had that kind of day huh?
Yeah... I'm beat. Lol
Me too. I kind of had a feeling I would be after that exam. It was pretty draining.
I want to watch something but my head feels kind of heavy.
You okay?
I'm good. Working on this new house a bit. Then probably head to bed.
Are you doing research?
We have. We have prints for he house, but no one can decide on the opening staircase.
Is it up to you now?
Nah, we're all taking about it.
You should get the staircase like the one in Harry Pottet!
*Potter
Lol, I'll find a way for it to move like that too.
You know what?? Since you're building your house, you should model it after Hogwarts!
Lol. Wouldn't that be a house.
